1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
I tracked my energy for 7
days. The pattern was obvious.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
I always thought my energy was random. Good
days, bad days, no rhyme or reason.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
After 7 days of logging when I crashed, when I
felt sharp, a clear pattern emerged: same time, every day.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Track your energy at 10 AM, 2 PM, and
6 PM for 7 days. You'll see it too.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
I built an app that does this
for you. 30 seconds to start. Free.

